name: Test Report
query:
SELECT 
    stock_entry.type as "Entry Type:Select/Consume Receive Transfer:100",
    stock_entry.entry_date as "Date:Date/:100",
    stock_entry.entry_time as "Time:Time/:100",
    ledger.item as "Item:Link/Item:100",
    ledger.from_warehouse as "Source Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:200",
    ledger.to_warehouse as "Destination Warehouse:Link/Warehouse:200",
    ledger.quantity as "Quantity:Int/:100"
FROM
  `tabStock Entry` stock_entry 
   LEFT JOIN `tabStock Ledger Entry` ledger
   ON stock_entry.name = ledger.parent
